Download tar file for postman
untar with command tar -xvz postman.tar
move Postman to /opt sudo mv Postman /opt/
create symlink sudo ln -s /opt/Postma/postman usr/local/bin/postman
Create desktop file
home/usr/.local/share/applications/postman.desktop
[Desktop Entry]
Name = Postman
Exec = /opt/Postman/Postman
Icon = /opt/Postman/app/resources/app/assets/icon.png
Type = Application
category = Devlopment;
